tid":1754043,"uid":53870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4876f238c503df67b84976a1ead717637a09f91","tid":1754043,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"文宣要重建呀"},{"pid":"718aafda028738d3601f7467127ef10390173560","tid":1754043,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"多謝文宣既手捉"},{"pid":"b497d6e20e004696a7d4ab6d97edb2a07356f1f7","tid":1754043,"uid":127807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9dc35358392713d91e3b21edad25a3fd1fa57a2","tid":1754043,"uid":9004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 <br />\n行過好多地方有時會見到啲廢老廢中企定定係到睇文宣 <br />\n令到佢地開始睇到真相覺醒<br />\n見到隔離po講彩雲選區 <br />\n好多老人家去投 但3席都贏<br />\n反映到文宣既助力之下起到好大既作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後 呢場仗未完 <br />\n跟住仲要擴大黃色經濟圈 區選後地區工作<br />\n各區巴絲得閒都去幫下自己區既新區議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:50:55.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n借位一用.......<br />\n<br />\n集中討論-----<br />\n[警世] 致各位今次當選區議員<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1753634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1753634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------<br />\n希望有人可以代筆一封正式EMAIL<br />\n最好中文掂既寫手去做(我中文唔好, 希望有高手)<br />\n情理兼備比我地去改<br />\n再EMAIL比自己區議員<br />\n佢地唔敢唔做野<br />\n叫佢地半年內公開PROPOSAL<br />\n點樣去改革社區同埋18區既區議會<br />\n<br />\n要做執政聯盟啦--- 如下<br />\n當選咗嘅區議員肯行多一步 政府即刻冇棋<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1753383/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1753383/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆可以各區都正式比個位<br />\n唔準差人拉<br />\n有得諗架<br />\n<br />\n另外請番手足亦係一件要做既事<br />\n比佢地做SUPPORT TEAM<br />\n<br />\n另外要查突出既選舉舞弊事件<br />\n焗住個制度要改善<br />\n唔好等馮鏵無野做<br />\n<br />\n更多意見包括五大訴求, 建立地區黃色經濟圈等<br />\n挾住區選民意 識得玩可以好好玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1753288/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1753288/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n降溫期思考, 如何利用勝選<br />\n警世 運動已經再次進入降溫期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1753702/page/1?post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1753702/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"65b80c692c592d2e3e21fed0184cb0caf6cfcc3c","tid":1754043,"uid":9004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f052a7d858a7a3b6a9b452c9a53416dad32a263","tid":1754043,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:46:01.000Z","msg":"其實區議員可唔可以設立社區連儂牆 將連儂牆合法化？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"都有諗過 有打算問下自己個區個區議員 <br />\n就算合法化唔到 都要保護佢 唔好再被班仆街拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5e18f3d19e7c4aaf3c513fb41522c0d1d6a616","tid":1754043,"uid":9004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"718aafda028738d3601f7467127ef10390173560","tid":1754043,"uid":10788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:49:49.000Z","msg":"多謝文宣既手捉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"文宣 網軍既手足 多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842ebcfcd0af2fa8d14f7a9df5878a0c8de7eb53","tid":1754043,"uid":9004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 文宣繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dedb8b5c37768019dd262196e171646820349b0c","tid":1754043,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"繼續做文宣"},{"pid":"9d7d83388b60f075780cc133ca3e3eab58d71acb","tid":1754043,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"